summary: THE REAR "RACETRACK" TAIL LAMP WHICH SPANS THE LIFTGATE FILLS WITH WATER.  THIS IS THE SECOND TAIL LAMP ASSEMBLY ON MY VEHICLE.  THE FIRST ONE WAS REPLACED BY DODGE UNDER WARRANTY.  LESS THAN 1 YEAR LATER, THE REPLACEMENT IS ALSO LEAKING.  SEVERAL REPORTS OF WATER IN THE LENS CAUSING ULTIMATE FAILURE OF THE ELECTRONICS AND THE LAMP.
